{"tid":1544341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌仔，NGO 制服member，想屌一屌消防處話數錯人嘅講法","createTime":"2019-09-05T13:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:29:20.000Z","uid":257163,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d02a358c1c96e5fd45383e45cb3d93e91c26b3dc","tid":1544341,"uid":257163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"有乜可能 ，loading officer 廢㗎？ 有幾多傷者上邊架車去邊間醫院都係佢負責㗎喎？拒絕救護服務要填form加簽名先走得㗎喎？同埋要即場埋數，埋完數先收車㗎喎，有咩可能出錯？一個都已經好大獲，仲錯三個？<br />\n<br />\nALP一大班人睇住，831係救護加SxJxxn到場救援，基本上一入去已經係分曬流mark曬人數，根本無可能俾傷者自己偷走到，亦無可能有人偷走ALO唔知。SxJxxn亦無可能會俾任何patient自行離去，因為SxJxxn無人孭得起（release人嘅決定係由消防處嘅救護負責）<br />\n<br />\n根本就無可能會數錯人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oT4dK6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoT4dK6v.png&h=9d35ef27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"0a43ca04609b8d4bfe398964bccc4dac70dd9663","tid":1544341,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d616638b1fb09333fa27280b1e55e2ec2253af82","tid":1544341,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e0bf9090fc0a360a7bbed80c4ed4f3ec6b522c","tid":1544341,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82dbe77e1bd9e1562fe164ef34a6977da0f2dac5","tid":1544341,"uid":257163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"入到黎嘅幫手推一推好唔好？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/squpRVM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsqupRVM.png&h=95b592fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4cab9f72c3024ba7154f0910cf28399b6b793e3","tid":1544341,"uid":101671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec42c0bc0a30946222224d3cac1c7bf086c42995","tid":1544341,"uid":101671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"